Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,that blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:37.18,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With special permission from Captain Global,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:41.56,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru and Minmay fly out to visit\NMinmay's parents in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:47.90,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There, Minmay is reunited with her cousin\NKaifun, who has long been out of touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.15,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at UN Forces High Command,\NMisa and Captain Global
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.75,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,presented their information on\Nthe Zentradi forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:57.43,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but their lack of evidence caused\Nthem to be met with disbelief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:01.89,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, they were refused to allow the\Ncivilians aboard the Macross to disembark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:06.05,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(68,134)}KUNG-FU DANDY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair! How can they not\Nlet us off the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's just typical of those people\Nat High Command!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:16.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're nothing but a bunch\Nof hard-headed idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to agree to this, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!\NYou'll fight this, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, just carry out your assigned duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to figure out how to\Nbreak this news to the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He won't even listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:47.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa, the captain strongly\Nobjected to this at High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:51.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Objected?\NAs a soldier... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:56.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,High Command is nothing\Nbut a bunch of thugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go into town and\nblow off some steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No objections here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welc...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:16.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.29,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dreaming, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a dream, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.73,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're making me cry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Hikaru, you must be feeling\Nawkward seeing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.83,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking well, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:02.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:04.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:19.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That damn fool kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we can eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sure {\i1}smells{\i0} good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I could eat anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had any food since the\Nrations we brought ran out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how do we get it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be an\Naccess port anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.10,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Loli, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.30,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:57.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to eat that, you\Nmust really be starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.63,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NInside, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something to eat.\NC'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:04.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NWhat's all the excitement about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NOver here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's 1st Lt. Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is rare, Max.\NYou hanging out with Captain Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wandering around town and\Nthey sort of made me join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:43.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Ichijo, what's all this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:50.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's cousin, I mean her uncle's son,\Nleft home a long time ago, but now he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So all his friends in the neighborhood\Ndecided to have a get-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!\NHe's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.82,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Riber...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, Kim's drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well your eyes are practically sparkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Ichijo!\NWhat's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:24.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lynn Kaifun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, what a cool name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's aunt looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.94,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Li'l Hikaru!\NAre these friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a bunch of nice-lookin' ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaifun!\NYou got some more guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you all could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:59.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See, Kaifun? You may hate the military,\Nbut it's got some real cuties in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:04.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NDid I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave you kids to yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See ya 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.09,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You dislike the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:16.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NI don't believe in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting accomplishes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All war ever leads to is destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"All war ever leads to is destruction..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:29.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I joined because I like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating Kaifun's homecoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! My TV show's coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.73,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could someone turn on the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And at the top of the charts,\NMiss Lynn Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.42,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:01.66,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!\NMinmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.47,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid desce-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We interrupt this song to bring\Nyou a special report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:10.34,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,According to a statement from Captain Global,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross will be undergoing\Nquarantine procedures,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,meaning that no civilians will be\Nallowed to leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:22.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}What did he just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is, of course, a temporary measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:29.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens are asked to remain calm and\Ngo about their normal business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:33.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We finally get back to Earth and\Nthey won't let us off the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are they quarantining us for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.16,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I want an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We now return to the song,\Nalready in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:47.96,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are they kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:55.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He could've come up with\Na better way of telling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder these people are angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:00.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think they're just going to accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's right!\NWe've got some soldiers in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have them explain what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well? You gonna explain\Nthis to us or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I don't know what's going on either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\NIs this how law-abiding citizens act?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down? You think we can take\Nsomething like this calmly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's your fault we lost our homes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.82,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We finally get back to Earth, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We get back, but...!\NYou won't let us off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just a temporary measure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.30,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's the same thing the military always says!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:44.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"You'll be back on Earth real soon."\N"You'll be off the ship real soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're sick of you people lying to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:49.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold 'em hostage and make\Nthe military let us off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:55.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:09:59.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what will happen if you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:22.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun...you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun, you were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.16,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was Chinese kung-fu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and he only used defensive\Ntechniques too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Chinese-style kung-fu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:49.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tough for a guy\Nwho claims to hate fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't use it to hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.05,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ri... Mr. Kaifun, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me. I'd accept it if you\Nweren't a soldier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NKaifun hates military people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.63,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, not so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.16,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NKamujin went out in an assault craft?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that foolish child...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should punish him a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.63,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, an unidentified flying object\Nis headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Altitude 12,000... 11,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:13.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On its current trajectory, it will land\N12 km away at 1 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take us to alert condition B at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And recall Captain Hayase here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:22.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy vessel descending!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:29.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it will splash down\Nat point K-32, R-56.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fire interceptor missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:33.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're after the Macross, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:40.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, the Macross is a burden that\Nthe Earth just can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes until it reaches estimated\Nlanding coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.11,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"All war ever leads to is destruction."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.07,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Misa?\NMisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, why are you so distracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.94,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You finally found a boyfriend worth\Ndaydreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.73,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming message from\NUN Forces High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They have launched interceptor missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.27,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not killing us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.22,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But not letting us live either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!\NAren't we going to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:37.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're not allowed to touch\Nthis planet, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the planet isn't our target?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie teams, first wave: launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship has launched flying battle pods!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:29.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have to light a fire under their ass\Nsomehow, and get them back into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:35.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A large number of battle pods are headed for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's turning into a close-quarters fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Move the Spartan teams out onto the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:41.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.87,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid Minmay. What's so\Ngood about that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:49.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Spartan teams, stand by in blocks 7, 9, and 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:53.09,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, provide support to block 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:02.92,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How many do we have to shoot down before\Nthey stop coming, Capt. Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she would bite my head\Noff for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, provide support\Nfor block 7 at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:00.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:01.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:02.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.73,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A second enemy wave is approaching\Nat high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:22.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your objective is to stop Kamujin's\Nunauthorized attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Under no circumstances are you\Nto attack the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're not to attack the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:30.10,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be a little difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See? We've already disobeyed the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your attack at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a clear violation of your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A violation of my orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just attacking the enemy vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't laid a single finger on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think arguing over\Nsemantics will work with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.73,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Return at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine!\NI'll come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Assault force, retreat at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!\NWe're quittin' so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:14.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice!\NCommander Lap'Lamiz gave us a direct order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but don't forget to leave\Nthem our souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, like I could forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy vessel is on a collision course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide run, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare a Daedalus Attack at once!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.73,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:55.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all stations!\NAttention, all stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:10.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine.\NI wasn't too close to the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't even touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:20.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Team, attack the approaching\Nenemy ships at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:21.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've got some fast ones on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You go after that other one, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:58.58,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Co... Commence Daedalus Attack in twenty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:35.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus Attack in eight seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:41.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:42.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:43.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:43.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:44.74,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:46.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:53.57,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,M...Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It punched through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Launching missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:31.92,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus Attack, phase two was a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship has been obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:52.16,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!\NThey blew up my assault craft!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:55.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin, it seems your present didn't reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:01.23,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sent down a recovery craft to pick\Nyou up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy forces are retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Should we pursue them, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no pursuit.\NThe battle's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:23.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But maintain alert for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:24.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:27.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Captain Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.63,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Report to your quarters at once.\NYou're taking some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:33.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.17,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Fighting accomplishes nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:48.26,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"How many do we have to shoot down\Nbefore they stop coming?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:53.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!\NI don't know anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:57.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,except that Kaifun is not Riber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(299,459)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.42,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:44.10,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Zentradi forces ace pilot, Milia,\Nengaged in heated aerial combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:47.16,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru is in serious condition\Nafter having been shot down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:50.09,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He is taken to the operating room,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:53.84,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and in a half-conscious state,\Nhe is tormented by nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.69,0:23:57.79,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:59.23,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"PHANTASM"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:02.46,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(72,122)}PHANTASM
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:23.17,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.53,0:24:29.87,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:36.54,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:44.15,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:50.87,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.26,0:24:56.91,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:25:04.44,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.67,0:25:15.69,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
